item.title: BAUS 40 Sunnyvale: Gameplay footage
item.description: A little while ago I was at Bay Area Ultra Stock’s 40th meetup and managed to record a few of the games. Played at Braly Elementary school in Sunnyvale California. For these games I was playing with my Pump Skewer by SillyButts designs. All parts were printed on my modified Ender3V2.
